<dl id="n09106f"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n09" href="#n09106f">N09 (VI.B.1)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n09all.htm#n09106f"> 106(f)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Malachy Cistercian / <font face="wake">+</font> Clairvaux / S Bernard </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: Cistercians = Grey or White monks. One of their daughter-houses was in Clairvaux. St Malachy died there in 1148, in the arms of St Bernard. </mm> </dd></dl>
